        <profile name="Weapon Sentinel" typeId="f887-5881-0e6d-755c" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="2ca9-0d14-5b24-1923">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Ability" typeId="3467-0678-083e-eb50">Whenever you&apos;re selecting a valid target, if this operative has a Conceal order, it cannot use Light terrain for cover. While this can allow this operative to be targeted (assuming it&apos;s visible), it doesn&apos;t remove its cover save (if any).</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Steadfast" typeId="f887-5881-0e6d-755c" typeName="Abilities" hidden="false" id="8f11-efd6-358b-275a">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Ability" typeId="3467-0678-083e-eb50">Whenever determining control of a marker, you can treat this operative&apos;s APL stat as 3. If you do, this takes precedence over all other rules, meaning any changes to its APL stat are ignored for this.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
